{
  "page": "Capture of Harrenhal",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> The title of this article is conjecture and may be subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Capture of Harrenhal</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannister</a> victory</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/33px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png\" width=\"33\" height=\"36\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/50px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/66px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a></b>/ <a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing\">House Baratheon of King's Landing</a>:<br />\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Lannister.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/30px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/45px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/60px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">Westerlands</a>, led by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Clegane\" title=\"House Clegane\">House Clegane</a></li></ul></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Brave_Companions.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Brave Companions.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/Brave_Companions.svg/30px-Brave_Companions.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/24/Brave_Companions.svg/45px-Brave_Companions.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/24/Brave_Companions.svg/60px-Brave_Companions.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Brave_Companions\" title=\"Brave Companions\">Brave Companions</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Clegane.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Clegane.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b6/House_Clegane.svg/20px-House_Clegane.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b6/House_Clegane.svg/30px-House_Clegane.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b6/House_Clegane.svg/40px-House_Clegane.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/File:Brave_Companions.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Brave Companions.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/Brave_Companions.svg/20px-Brave_Companions.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/24/Brave_Companions.svg/30px-Brave_Companions.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/24/Brave_Companions.svg/40px-Brave_Companions.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Vargo_Hoat\" title=\"Vargo Hoat\">Vargo Hoat</a>†</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown total<br /><a href=\"/index.php/Mountain%27s_men\" title=\"Mountain&#39;s men\">Mountain's men</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Remnants of Harrenhal garrison</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Not significant</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/Vargo_Hoat\" title=\"Vargo Hoat\">Vargo Hoat</a>†<br />Remnants of garrison</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>capture of Harrenhal</b> occurs during the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a> and his men retake <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a> after the <a href=\"/index.php/Fighting_at_the_fords_of_the_Trident\" title=\"Fighting at the fords of the Trident\">fighting at the fords of the Trident</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Prelude\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Prelude</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Capture\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Capture</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prelude\">Prelude</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Capture_of_Harrenhal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Prelude\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a>, having decided to switch his allegiance from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a>, sends a third of the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">northern</a> foot to <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_Duskendale\" title=\"Battle at Duskendale\">defeat at Duskendale</a>. Roose leaves Harrenhal to its new lord, <a href=\"/index.php/Vargo_Hoat\" title=\"Vargo Hoat\">Vargo Hoat</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Brave_Companions\" title=\"Brave Companions\">Brave Companions</a>, as he goes north to the <a href=\"/index.php/Twins\" title=\"Twins\">Twins</a> for the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Wedding\" title=\"Red Wedding\">Red Wedding</a> with the remaining northmen. There is <a href=\"/index.php/Fighting_at_the_fords_of_the_Trident\" title=\"Fighting at the fords of the Trident\">fighting at the Trident</a> while Roose is on his way to the wedding, as he allows Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a> to overwhelm his rearguard at the <a href=\"/index.php/Ruby_ford\" title=\"Ruby ford\">ruby ford</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Vargo suffers from infection after his ear is bitten off by <a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_of_Tarth\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brienne of Tarth\">Brienne of Tarth</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Capture\">Capture</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Capture_of_Harrenhal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Capture\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Under orders from Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>, Gregor and the <a href=\"/index.php/Mountain%27s_men\" title=\"Mountain&#39;s men\">Mountain's men</a> retake Harrenhal. Almost all<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos74.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos74.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> of Vargo's Brave Companions flee before he arrives, allowing Gregor to retake the castle easily.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> A cook, angered by having his foot cut off by Vargo, opens a postern gate to the Lannister men,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos74.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos74.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> and Vargo is found delirious and alone in the Hall of a Hundred Hearths.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Gregor's band butchers most inhabitants of the castle, although survivors include the cook,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos74.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos74.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> the <a href=\"/index.php/Smith\" title=\"Smith\">smith</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Ben_Blackthumb\" title=\"Ben Blackthumb\">Ben Blackthumb</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> and some women<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos74.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos74.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> such as <a href=\"/index.php/Pia\" title=\"Pia\">Pia</a> whom the Lannisters rape repeatedly.\n</p><p>Gregor butchers Vargo, known as the goat, removing his limbs one at a time and sealing the wounds with fire to stop Vargo from bleeding to death. Gregor then has the limbs cooked and forces Vargo to eat his own flesh. Gregor also has his northern captives from the Trident, such as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Wylis_Manderly\" title=\"Wylis Manderly\">Wylis Manderly</a>, have a taste of \"roast goat\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Capture_of_Harrenhal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a> is again in the hands of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a>. Members of the <a href=\"/index.php/Brave_Companions\" title=\"Brave Companions\">Brave Companions</a> are on the run throughout the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>. When Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> returns to Harrenhal after the death of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a>, the only servants remaining of those who had once served Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Shella_Whent\" title=\"Shella Whent\">Shella Whent</a> are the maimed cook, <a href=\"/index.php/Ben_Blackthumb\" title=\"Ben Blackthumb\">Ben Blackthumb</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Pia\" title=\"Pia\">Pia</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Capture_of_Harrenhal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Tywin</b>: I mean to offer generous terms. Any castle that yields to us will be spared, save one.<br />\n</p><p><b>Tyrion</b>: <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a>?<br />\n</p>\n<b>Tywin</b>: The realm is best rid of these <a href=\"/index.php/Brave_Companions\" title=\"Brave Companions\">Brave Companions</a>. I have commanded Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor</a> to put the castle to the sword.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Sandor</b>: So <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor</a> took <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a>?<br />\n<b>Polliver</b>: Didn't require much taking. <a href=\"/index.php/Brave_Companions\" title=\"Brave Companions\">The sellswords</a> fled as soon as they knew we were coming, all but a few. One of the cooks opened a postern gate for us, to get back at <a href=\"/index.php/Vargo_Hoat\" title=\"Vargo Hoat\">Hoat</a> for cutting off his foot. We kept him to cook for us, a couple wenches to warm our beds, and put all the rest to the sword.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos74.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos74.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Polliver\" title=\"Polliver\">Polliver</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Capture_of_Harrenhal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_60\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 60\">Chapter 60</a>, Tyrion VIII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span cla